metadata.name: i can see you
metadata.description:
entangled in bones and skulls, chains wrap the scenery smooth like silk, the hollow silence leaving goosebumps on your skin .. you see her .. can she see you?

'' i can see you . '' you hear her faintly from across the way, but as if she was whispering in your ear .. 

'' but .. why can you see me? '' 

//

digital illustration. csp. 03292022.
